snippet.title: DENNY CAKNAN - TUNGGAL EKA  (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
DENNY CAKNAN - TUNGGAL EKA  (Official Music Video)
Produksi : DC Production
Penyanyi : Denny Caknan
Penulis lagu : Denny Caknan, Rijal Pamungkas, Shadeva Wijaya, Soepardi
Penata musik : Bayu onyonk, Soepardi, Rijal Pamungkas

♫ LIRIK ♫

Aku nebak
isine pandongamu
wis tak siapke
kado nggo sliramu
aku ngukir
kata - kata romantis
sing iso
nyenengke kowe sing manis

Seksine dunyo lan langit gedhene rasaku
tunggal eka mring sliramu
panjang umurmu

Tak usahane panyuwunmu
tak pasrahke jantung atiku
nganti nemoni lelayu

Sing apik - apik ya sayang
ning dino istimewa iki
dongaku langgeng tresno abadi

Semerbak wangine ambeganmu
gugah rasa tembok gairahku
manise suara rayuanmu
negeske kowe ra iso kelangan aku 

yang dongaku sampean bahagia
kadoku terkesan biasa
rung iso ngenehi sing sempurna
selamat tambah usiyang
semoga umur panjang
ku harap bisa terkenang sayang

Copyright ©2025
DENNY CAKNAN


#DennyCaknan #TunggalEka #DC
========================================

snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— robert downey jr

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, Avengers: Doomsday positions itself as the opening act of the Multiverse Saga’s final confrontation, where Victor von Doom rises as a master of science and sorcery who believes the multiverse must be controlled to be saved. As Earth’s heroes stand divided, Sam Wilson’s Captain America attempts to rebuild the Avengers while rival teams and uneasy alliances complicate any hope of unity. The arrival of the Fantastic Four from another reality and the long-awaited emergence of the X-Men signal that the conflict can no longer be contained within a single universe. With incursions threatening to collapse entire timelines, Doom’s ideology challenges heroes and gods alike, drawing figures like Loki into a battle over who truly holds the right to shape existence. The story frames Doomsday as a turning point where legacy, power, and sacrifice collide, setting the stage for a multiversal reckoning that will define the future of the Marvel universe.

snippet.description:
NGEONG!! Buat Sirkuit BALAP Mobil Terbesar & Terpanjang Max Level 🔥🔥🔥 | Build a Racetrack Indonesia

Nama Game : Build a Racetrack
Link Game : https://www.roblox.com/games/102515807161964

🔰 Sekarang kalau mau record, bang Hayo kabarin lewat VOICE di Room Santuy yang ada di Discord. Jadwal ga tentu, tapi biasanya kalau sore sekitar jam 15.30 - 16.30 WIB. Baca lagi bagian bawah biar kalian benar-benar mengerti 🗿

Sebelum JOIN, tolong baca ini ya 🙏😁
✅ Izin sama orang tua & tanya boleh ga install dan main Discord? Btw, discord punya aturan kalau mau buat akun mesti umur 13+
✅ PENTING!! Ikut MABAR atau RECORD mungkin agak susah karena ramai yang tungguin bang Hayo, sedangkan game Roblox server-nya terbatas
✅ Record juga GA SELALU MABAR  karena beberapa game ga boleh rusuh & mesti diatur sebaik mungkin
✅ Kalau mau record, bang Hayo kabarin lewat voice "Room Santuy" di discord
✅ Ga bisa ADD karena sudah full. Satu-satunya solusi adalah FOLLOW akun Roblox bang Hayo dan nanti kalian bisa JOIN bang Hayo main. Lalu, kalau bang Hayo lagi AFK atau SERVER sudah penuh, teman-teman ga bisa join ya
✅ Kadang bang Hayo harus pakai LINK PRIVATE SERVER biar record-nya lebih lancar. Kirim link-nya di Discord & untuk cara JOIN baca di cara-ikut-record yang ada di Discord
✅ Baca PERATURAN GROUP & PERTANYAAN UMUM  di Discord untuk kepentingan bersama
✅ Di group ini kalian juga bisa mencari KAWAN yang mungkin cocok sama kalian dan bisa main bareng. Ga perlu fokus sama bang Hayo saja karena bang Hayo ga mampu standby 24 jam
✅ Mohon pengertiannya kalau ga berhasil JOIN bang Hayo karena server sudah FULL & sistemnya siapa cepat dia masuk dulu

🔰 Bang, kenapa ga bisa chat di Discord?
Untuk menjadi MEMBER di Discord, teman-teman harus tulis username Roblox yang AKTIF di nama-roblox & baca bagian peraturan-server

🔰 Bang, CARA JOIN gimana ya?
Bang Hayo sudah jelasin secara lengkap di Discord. Cari saja di channel cara-ikut-record biar kalian paham. Lalu, akun yang umurnya kurang dari 13 tahun akan agak sulit buat join karena peraturan terbaru Roblox
